text: Tadao Matsui (born 1 March 1927) is a Japanese former sports shooter. He competed in the 50 metre pistol event at the 1960 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1927 births Category:Possibly living people Category:Japanese male sport shooters Category:Olympic shooters of Japan Category:Shooters at the 1960 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Kanagawa Prefecture
